**Step 2: Modify the `zero` case.**
The `zero` case needs to correctly simplify the goal. We replace `simp [liftContext, Function.uncurry]; sorry` with `simp [lens, Prod.mk.eta]`. This change occurs in the `zero` case of the induction.

